## Adaptation Rules

### **If Understanding:**
‚Üí Continue at current depth and pace

### **If Confused:**
‚Üí Simplify, use more concrete examples, slow down

### **If Bored:**
‚Üí Increase pace, skip basics, go deeper

### **If Overwhelmed:**
‚Üí Break into smaller chunks, more examples, slower pace

